<b>Easy and Fast usage:<\b><br>
simply start your php script with:<br>
require(path to easymail.php);<br>
and then you are ready to use email($to,$subject,$message,$is_html);<br>
<b>Configuration</b><br>
Open config.json<br>
Enter all credentials and network settings.<br>
And you are ready to go!<br>